---
title: 12-cicd-pipeline-workflows/03-reusable-ci-guards
---
flowchart TD
    Start([Trigger: pipeline event])
    Validate{Inputs valid?}
    Run[Execute module workflow]
    Check{Exit code 0?}
    Persist[Insert audit-log row]
    Notify[Notify subscribers / emit metric]
    Fail[Emit AppError + exit non-zero]
    Done([End])

    Start --> Validate
    Validate -- yes --> Run --> Check
    Validate -- no  --> Fail --> Done
    Check -- yes --> Persist --> Notify --> Done
    Check -- no  --> Fail
